text: Bérengère Schuh is an archer from France. She was born on 13 June 1984. Schuh competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics, 2008 Summer Olympics, and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Bérengère SchuhBerengere SCHUH == References == Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:French archers Category:Olympic bronze medalists for France Category:People from Auxerre Category:Sportspeople from Bourgogne-Franche-Comté
